## Next Steps

To complete the Speed Insights setup:

1. **Enable Speed Insights in Vercel Dashboard**:
   - Navigate to your project in the Vercel dashboard
   - Select "Speed Insights" from the sidebar
   - Click the "Enable" button

2. **Deploy the Changes**:
   - Push this branch and merge the PR
   - Vercel will automatically deploy the changes

3. **View Performance Data**:
   - After deployment and user visits, access Speed Insights in your Vercel dashboard
   - Monitor Core Web Vitals and performance metrics

